snippet.title: Dungeon Train Oculus Quest VR Dungeon Crawler Train of Decay SideQuest Review Gameplay
snippet.description:
Dungeon Train Gameplay and Review for the Oculus Quest. This is a VR Dungeon Crawler in development found on SideQuest.

This Procedural VR Looter shows a lot of promise, but has a long way to go.

Song at the end:
Two Little Bums by The Great North Sound Society
